name: Resin Cuff links
description: A great pair of  brass ox cuff links with watch parts encased in resin.  Each pair has some differences and are unique.

name: Resin Heart Necklace
description: A fun heart necklace with vintage watch parts, encased in resin.  Each one varies in the color and shape of the watch face.

name: Watch Movement Locket Necklace
description: A vintage jeweled watch movement inset into a silver colored locket.  It comes on your choice of 17" black cord or 18" ball chain.

name: Five Watch Movement Round Bracelet
description: A fantastic bracelet with 5 18mm round movements.  It is 7 1/2" long and made from stainless steel.

name: Typewriter Key Locket
description:
A locket with a large vintage typewriter key inset into it.  The typewriter key is 18mm.  The necklace comes on your choice of 17" black cord or 18" ball chain.  

Your choice of black or cream key is available.

name: Time Watch Part Resin Necklace
description:
This is a really fun necklace of vintage watch gears, watch face and the word time in resin.  It is approximately 20mm wide on your choice of 17" black cord or 18" ball chain.  

If you want a longer or shorter ball chain, just add a comment in your payment.

name: Six Watch Movement Steampunk Bracelet
description: A lovely bracelet made with 6 vintage jeweled watch movements.  It measures 7.5" long.  The bracelet itself is made from stainless steel.

name: Recycled Steampunk Spinner Ring
description: A wonderful resin based ring with a spinning top.  Each piece spins easily and separately.  These are quite large, showcase rings measuring 24 mm around.  Base is adjustable and stainless steel.

name: Recycled Tin Spool Necklace
description: A beautiful vintage tin made into a spool.  We've added a wire spiral and 24" antiqued copper ball chain.  Each necklace is unique!  Contact me directly for current tins available.

name: Soda Pop Necklace
description: A wonderful vintage soda pop bottle cap made into this fun and funky necklace.  Perfect for the nostalgic buyer!  Each one is unique.  Contact me directly if you want a specific color or soda flavor.

name: Gold Winged Bug Steampunk (Watch Movement) Necklace
description: A wonderful Steampunk bug fashioned from a vintage watch movement.  It comes on 18" ball chain or an adjustable 17"-18" black leather cord.

name: Fancy Shift Typewriter Key Necklace
description: A wonderful filigree with either a floral or swirl background grace this vintage typewriter key.  Choose from 18" ball chain or 17"-18" adjustable black leather cord.

name: Propeller Watch Dial Locket Necklace
description:
A beautiful old watch dial topped with a great propeller compliment this wonderful vintage gold and copper locket. This is a larger piece measuring 1.5"...perfect for a larger photo. The quarter inside is to give you a visual idea of the inside size.

It comes on an 18" gold ball chain.

name: Movable Propeller Earrings in Gold or Silver
description: A wonderful pair of propeller earrings.  The propellers are rotate (by your hand...they don't move on their own).  A fun pair of earrings!  Choose from gold or silver propellers.

name: Watch Movement Necklace with Half Circle Flourish
description: A vintage jeweled watch movement with a wonderful half circle flourish behind it!  Comes on an 18" ball chain or black leather cord.

name: Winged Watch Movement Steampunk Necklace
description: A fun necklace with wonderful wings!  Comes on 18" silver ball chain or black leather cord.  Also available in silver wings!

name: Etched Pocket Watch Swirl Steampunk Necklace
description: A wonderful hand-etched vintage pocket watch piece highlighted with vintage gears and cogs.  Each piece is one of a kind!  Choose from 18" ball chain or 17"-18" black leather cord.

name: Steampunk Filligree Watch Movement Necklace
description: A beautiful movement with a flowery background watch movement (Steampunk) necklace.  The movement in each piece will vary from the one in the picture. Comes on an adjustable 17" - 18" black leather cord or 18" ball chain.

name: Winged Propeller Steampunk Necklace
description: A fun necklace with moving propeller!  Comes on 18" silver ball chain or black leather cord.

name: Beautiful Jeweled Watch Movement Steampunk Cuff Links
description: This is a beautiful pair of jeweled watch movements made into cuff links. They are perfect for formal attire and on a tuxedo!

name: Wire Wrapped Steampunk Watch Movement Necklace
description: A wonderful necklace made from a vintage watch movement. Beautiful on both sides. It measures 1". Choose from an adjustable 17" - 18" (based on where you clip at the chain) black leather cord or 18" silver ball chain.

name: Bezeled Steampunk Watch Movement Necklace
description: A beautiful bezel watch movement (Steampunk) necklace. The movement in each piece will vary from the one in the picture. Comes on an adjustable 17" - 18" black leather cord or 18" ball chain.

name: Leafy Wrapped Steampunk Watch Movement Necklace
description: A wonderful necklace made from a vintage watch movement. It measures 1" long by 1" wide (edge of the leaves).  The cording is adjustable 17" - 18" (based on where you clip at the chain) black leather cord. You can change the black cording to 18" silver ball chain.

name: Steampunk Stacked Gear Bracelet
description: This bracelets uses vintage gears, cogs, wheels and more to build a beautiful stacked style bracelet.  This bracelet has 12 rounds on an 7.5" stainless steel backing. This bracelet can easily be adjusted to be larger or smaller. Each one is one of a kind and unique!!

name: Jeweled Watch Movement Steampunk Bracelet
description: A lovely bracelet made with vintage jeweled watch movements.  It measures 7.5" long and is easily adjustable to be longer or shorter.

name: Jeweled Steampunk Watch Movement Earrings
description:
A lovely pair of watch movement earrings. I love the oval shape and swirling on the main spring cover. They measure just over .5".

A perfect gift!

name: Flower Steampunk Pocket Watch Gear Earrings
description: A lovely pair of earrings made from vintage pocket watch gears! The flowers measure .75" on stainless steel fish hooks.  Looks great with the Stacked Gear bracelet.

name: Non-Adjustable Steampunk Watch Movement Ring
description: The band is stainless steel (perfect for those with metal issues and you'll never have to clean it) and will be made in your size. The band measures 1/4" wide and has a very comfortable fit.  Movements available in round, oval or rectangle.  Email me with your size. Wholesale orders will receive an assortment of sizes unless otherwise specified.

name: Adjustable Jeweled Watch Movement Steampunk Ring
description: Choose from a rectangle, round or oval watch movement put on a wonderful adjustable stainless steel ring.

name: Steampunk Watch Movement Cuff Links and Tie Tack Set
description: This is a wonderful set of steampunk cuff links and a tie tack made from vintage jeweled watch movements. Have a complete set for a wedding, convention or special occasion!

name: Steampunk Watch Movement Propeller Cuff Links
description: A wonderful pair of cuff links perfect for your suits and tuxedos that have shirts with french cuffs.  A wonderful gift for a pilot!!  The propeller actually rotates!!  Choose from silver propellers or gold propellers.

name: Steampunk Watch Movement Propeller Tie Tack
description:
A fun tie tack! The base is a vintage watch movement with a movable propeller. Each tie tack has the shirt chain backing included! Perfect for the pilot or Steampunk enthusiast in your life! 

Choose from a gold or silver propeller.

name: Jeweled Watch Movement Steampunk Tie Tack
description: Gorgeous jeweled watch movement Steampunk tie tack. Great accessory for the person who already has cuff links!  Movements available in gold, silver or rose gold (copper).

name: Vintage Watch Case Bracelet
description: Vintage watch cases made into a great bracelet.  Wear as is or add fun stuff inside the case...including pictures!  Super cute and a great variety of things you can do with these!!  Measures approx 7.5" long.  Choose from silver or gold color.

name: Pocket Watch Collage Steampunk Necklace
description: A wonderful porcelain pocket watch dial that has been embellished with gears and etched pocket watch pieces.  Available on an 18" ball chain necklace or black leather cord.  Each piece is unique and one of a kind.  (piece shown has been sold).

name: Cupped and Riveted Watch Dial Face Necklace
description: We've taken vintage watch faces and wonderfully textured metal and cupped them to form this wonderful necklace.  Then we added a handmade textured bezel to complete the necklace.  Each one is one of a kind and unique!  Choose from 18" oxidized copper ball chain or an adjustable 17"-18" black leather cord.

name: Fancy Adjustable Watch Face Ring
description: A wonderful stainless steel adjustable ring adorned with an authentic vintage watch face.

name: Flower Watch Dial Necklace
description: A wonderful lens with a flower made from watch dials.  The center of the flower can be a typewriter key or a watch movement. You choose!  Comes on a 22" antiqued silver chain.

name: Watch Dial Steampunk Necklace
description: A lovely watch dial necklace with a frilly filigree in the background. It measures 1" across. Comes on an adjustable 17" - 18" black leather cord or it can be changed to an 18" ball chain necklace.

name: Small Watch Face Dial Bracelet
description: A wonderful watch face bracelet made from vintage watch dials. The large bracelet has 12 faces on an 7.5" stainless steel backing. Please note this bracelet can easily be adjusted larger or smaller. Each one is one of a kind and unique!!

name: Large Watch Dial Face Bracelet
description:
A wonderful watch face bracelet made from vintage watch dials.  The large bracelet has 6 faces on an 7.5" stainless steel backing.  Please note that the large bracelets can not be adjusted to be larger or smaller.  Each one is one of a kind and unique!!

Choose from: Round Dials or Square Dials.

name: Watch Dial Steampunk Earrings
description: Wonderful earrings all made from vintage watch dials.  Choose from large round dials, large square dials or art deco rectangle dials.

name: Adjustable Typewriter Ring
description:
A wonderful plain ring that is adjustable!  Choose from your initials, numbers/symbols or typewriter words like backspace, margin release and shift.  Email me directly with the key you'd like.

Choose from Black background or white (cream) background keys.

name: Vintage Typewriter Ring Black and White Your Choice of Letter or Number
description:
A great custom ring with your choice of letter or number. The ring is adjustable and stainless steel. Put the letter or number you'd like in the sellers note field. All of our jewelry is made from vintage typewriter keys and not reproduction keys.

Please note that there was no number 1 (there was only a 1 on a very few typewriters and it's fairly rare that I have it...when I do, I list it as its own listing).

Email me directly with letter desired or put in the notes field on your Paypal payment.

name: Vintage Typewriter Key Necklace You Choose ONE Letter
description: A great necklace with a real vintage typewriter key. Comes on an adjustable 17" - 18" black leather cord or 18" ball chain.  Choose from a black background key or white/cream key. Just put the letter you want in the note field on PayPal! Letters subject to availability.  The perfect gift!

name: Fancy Adjustable Typewriter Ring
description:
A wonderful stainless steel adjustable ring adorned with an authentic vintage typewriter key.  Choose from your initial, backspace, margin release, tab, shift or numbers/symbols.  Please email me with the key you want!  

Choose from black background or white (cream) background keys.

name: XO Hugs and Kisses Typewriter Necklace
description:
A wonderful gift made from vintage typewriter keys. It comes on an 18" ball chain necklace or you can opt for an adjustable 17"-18" black leather cord.

Hug and kiss the one you're with! 

Because every typewriter manufacturer used different fonts, font sizes and backgrounds, it is likely your necklace will vary from the ones seen in the photo.  

Choose your colors!  Choices are black background, cream background or white background. 

(shown with the black background)

name: XO Hugs and Kisses Typewriter Earrings
description:
Your vintage hugs and kisses earrings measure 15 mm around and are encased in a beautiful vintage inspired backing.  They are much lighter than you would imagine so they won't hurt your ears when you wear them.  This is one of our best sellers!

Because every typewriter manufacturer used different fonts, font sizes and backgrounds, it is likely your earrings will vary from the ones seen in the photo.  

Choose your colors!  Choices are black background, cream background or white background. 

(shown with the black background)

name: Flying Typewriter Key Necklace
description: A vintage typewriter key with cute wings. It measures 1.25 from wing tip to wing tip. It comes on an 18" stainless steel ball chain or a 17"-18" adjustable black leather cord.

options.name: Black Key on Black Leather Cord

name: Vintage Typewriter Bracelet
description:
A wonderful vintage typewriter key bracelet. The keys are from a pre-1950's typewriter. We only use authentic typewriter keys with the original lettering. It measures 7.5" long and has a stainless steel backing.

Choose your background color: 
black with white letters
white or cream with black letters
variegated (alternating) keys

name: Vintage Typewriter Tie Tack Black and White Your Choice of Letter or Number
description:
A great custom tie tack with your choice of letter or number. Put the letter or number you'd like in the note field in Paypal. All of our jewelry is made from vintage typewriter keys and not reproduction keys.

Please note that there was no number 1 (there was only a 1 on a very few typewriters and it's fairly rare that I have it...when I do, I list it as its own listing).

name: Custom Vintage Typewriter Cuff Links your choice of letters
description:
Pick your own letters, numbers or punctuation for a pair of cuff links using vintage typewriter keys! I use only 1940's (or earlier) typewriters. Just send me a note with your purchase on what letters you want. These make a great gift for that special someone!

Please note I'm currently out of the letters S,M,J.

name: Vintage Typewriter Bookmark Black and White Your Choice of Letter or Number
description:
A great custom bookmark with your choice of letter or number. Hangs perfectly over the side of the book regardless of the book size. Put the letter or number you'd like in the sellers note field. All of our jewelry is made from vintage typewriter keys and not reproduction keys.

Please note that there was no number 1 (there was only a 1 on a very few typewriters and it's fairly rare that I have it...when I do, I list it as its own listing).

name: Riveted and Stamped Collage Bracelet
description: Wonderful squares of vintage copper etched and then adorned with a variety of wonderful copper, brass and silver pieces.  Each one is unique.  Measures 7.5".

name: Riveted and Stamped Watch Dial Collage Earrings
description: A perfect compliment to the rivets collage necklace.  These wonderful earrings are fun and each pair are unique.

name: Key Angel Necklace
description: A wonderful vintage key with wings and watch dial.  Comes on a large link antiqued silver chain.  Each one is unique and one of a kind.

name: Skeleton Key Necklace
description:
A wonderful vintage skeleton key with a charm and Swarovski crystal.  Charms and color of crystals vary by necklace.  Charm design choices include:

Paris
Heart
Wings
Clock
Lock
Misc

Please email if you have a specific theme in mind.

Comes on 22" ball chain.

name: Vintage Lock and Key Necklace
description: If you love Warehouse 13, you'll love this lock and key necklace like Claudia wears in Syfy's Warehouse 13. It comes on a 17 - 18" black leather cord.
